[
  {
    "text": "Thank you for joining our session.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=0"
  },
  {
    "text": "Today, we'd like to provide step-by-step guidance ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=2"
  },
  {
    "text": "to show you some of the ways you can manage price changes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=5"
  },
  {
    "text": "for your auto-renewable subscriptions ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=8"
  },
  {
    "text": "in App Store Connect.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=10"
  },
  {
    "text": "I'm Bryan and I'm part of the App Store Monetization team ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=12"
  },
  {
    "text": "based in Cupertino.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=15"
  },
  {
    "text": "App Store Connect provides many tools to help you manage ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=18"
  },
  {
    "text": "your subscriptions pricing on the App Store.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=21"
  },
  {
    "text": "To name a few examples, you can use App Store Connect ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=24"
  },
  {
    "text": "to create subscription offers to help you acquire, retain, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=28"
  },
  {
    "text": "and win back customers.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=32"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can also use it to set the price of your subscription ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=35"
  },
  {
    "text": "across all available territories.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=38"
  },
  {
    "text": "It gives you the ability to increase or decrease the price ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=42"
  },
  {
    "text": "of your subscription for new customers ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=45"
  },
  {
    "text": "as well as manage price increases for customers ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=48"
  },
  {
    "text": "on preserved pricing.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=51"
  },
  {
    "text": "And today's presentation ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=54"
  },
  {
    "text": "is focused on these last two capabilities.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=55"
  },
  {
    "text": "Today we'll walk through the necessary steps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=60"
  },
  {
    "text": "to create and manage your price increases.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=62"
  },
  {
    "text": "We'll show you how to remove preserved pricing ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=66"
  },
  {
    "text": "from specific cohorts, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=68"
  },
  {
    "text": "how to initiate a price decrease, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=71"
  },
  {
    "text": "and finally, we'll discuss how you can edit ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=74"
  },
  {
    "text": "upcoming price changes before they go live.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=77"
  },
  {
    "text": "So let's get started by simulating the steps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=81"
  },
  {
    "text": "you would take in order to initiate a price increase ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=83"
  },
  {
    "text": "on your subscription.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=86"
  },
  {
    "text": "This process will begin in the subscription pricing section ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=89"
  },
  {
    "text": "of App Store Connect, which can be found ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=93"
  },
  {
    "text": "within the details of your auto-renewable subscription.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=95"
  },
  {
    "text": "Start by clicking on the plus button.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=99"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then, click on Plan Subscription Price Change ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=102"
  },
  {
    "text": "from the drop-down menu.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=105"
  },
  {
    "text": "You'll then be prompted to select the territories ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=107"
  },
  {
    "text": "where you want to edit pricing.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=110"
  },
  {
    "text": "Once you've made your selection, click Next.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=113"
  },
  {
    "text": "You'll then choose the date you'd like to begin ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=118"
  },
  {
    "text": "your price increase, followed by the currency and new price.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=120"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then, click Next.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=125"
  },
  {
    "text": "Apple automatically calculates the prices for all territories ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=129"
  },
  {
    "text": "based on your chosen price point, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=132"
  },
  {
    "text": "determined by the most recent foreign exchange rates ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=135"
  },
  {
    "text": "and taxation.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=138"
  },
  {
    "text": "However, you still have the option to set ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=140"
  },
  {
    "text": "different price points per territory in the event ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=142"
  },
  {
    "text": "it's more appropriate to your services value in those markets.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=145"
  },
  {
    "text": "Once you've completed your review of pricing ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=150"
  },
  {
    "text": "in each region, click Next.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=152"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then, you'll be prompted with the option ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=155"
  },
  {
    "text": "of how to manage pricing for your current subscribers.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=158"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can either keep the current price for existing subscribers ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=162"
  },
  {
    "text": "so that anyone who has subscribed before the start date ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=166"
  },
  {
    "text": "of the price change won't be affected, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=168"
  },
  {
    "text": "or apply the new price to your existing subscribers.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=171"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's review that first scenario more closely.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=176"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you don't want to apply your price increase ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=181"
  },
  {
    "text": "to your existing subscribers -- for example, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=183"
  },
  {
    "text": "to keep existing customer commitments or reduce churn -- ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=186"
  },
  {
    "text": "select Preserve current price for existing subscribers.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=190"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then, click Next.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=194"
  },
  {
    "text": "You'll then be prompted to review and confirm ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=197"
  },
  {
    "text": "the list of planned price changes.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=200"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, let's discuss how you would apply your price increase ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=203"
  },
  {
    "text": "to your existing subscribers.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=206"
  },
  {
    "text": "By selecting \"Apply price increase ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=209"
  },
  {
    "text": "to existing subscribers,\" you will have the option ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=212"
  },
  {
    "text": "to apply the price change to existing subscribers ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=214"
  },
  {
    "text": "who are paying the price of your subscription ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=218"
  },
  {
    "text": "currently displayed on the App Store.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=220"
  },
  {
    "text": "Any subscribers on previously preserved prices ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=222"
  },
  {
    "text": "won't be affected.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=225"
  },
  {
    "text": "The App Store will automatically communicate to any customer ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=228"
  },
  {
    "text": "impacted by the price increase ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=232"
  },
  {
    "text": "that a change is scheduled to occur.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=234"
  },
  {
    "text": "Depending on certain criteria, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=236"
  },
  {
    "text": "customers will either be notified or asked to consent ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=238"
  },
  {
    "text": "before renewing at a higher price.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=242"
  },
  {
    "text": "Customer consent is required in certain markets ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=245"
  },
  {
    "text": "as well as in scenarios when large ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=248"
  },
  {
    "text": "or frequent price increases occur.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=250"
  },
  {
    "text": "In the event your price change meets these criteria, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=253"
  },
  {
    "text": "App Store Connect will provide an indicator icon ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=256"
  },
  {
    "text": "noting consent is required.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=259"
  },
  {
    "text": "Apple will then inform affected customers through email, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=261"
  },
  {
    "text": "push notification, and in-app messaging ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=265"
  },
  {
    "text": "to ask them to agree to the new price.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=268"
  },
  {
    "text": "You also have the option to use ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=271"
  },
  {
    "text": "the showPriceConsentIfNeeded() method ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=272"
  },
  {
    "text": "to surface the in-app consent sheet at specific times.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=275"
  },
  {
    "text": "In the event of the notification flow, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=280"
  },
  {
    "text": "Apple will send an email to all customers and provide ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=282"
  },
  {
    "text": "an in-app message to customers on iOS 13.4 and later, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=285"
  },
  {
    "text": "at least 30 days prior to the price increase.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=290"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then, seven days prior to the price increase, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=293"
  },
  {
    "text": "if a customer has not yet viewed an in-app message ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=296"
  },
  {
    "text": "and has push notifications enabled, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=299"
  },
  {
    "text": "they will also receive a push notification on iOS, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=302"
  },
  {
    "text": "iPadOS, and macOS.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=306"
  },
  {
    "text": "The price will then automatically increase ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=308"
  },
  {
    "text": "on day 30, unless a customer chooses ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=310"
  },
  {
    "text": "to cancel their subscription before then.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=313"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now jumping back into App Store Connect.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=316"
  },
  {
    "text": "When choosing to apply your price increase ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=319"
  },
  {
    "text": "to existing subscribers, you'll be prompted to select ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=321"
  },
  {
    "text": "the regions where you would like to schedule your price change.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=324"
  },
  {
    "text": "Once selected, click Next.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=327"
  },
  {
    "text": "As mentioned, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=331"
  },
  {
    "text": "Apple automatically calculates the prices for all territories ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=332"
  },
  {
    "text": "based on your chosen price point.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=335"
  },
  {
    "text": "But you again have the option to set different prices ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=338"
  },
  {
    "text": "for specific territories.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=340"
  },
  {
    "text": "Once you've set any specific territory prices, click Next.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=344"
  },
  {
    "text": "You'll again be prompted to review ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=350"
  },
  {
    "text": "the list of planned price changes.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=351"
  },
  {
    "text": "And in the event you want to export the list, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=354"
  },
  {
    "text": "click Export as CSV in the top right.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=357"
  },
  {
    "text": "And once you're ready to initiate your price increase, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=361"
  },
  {
    "text": "click Confirm.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=364"
  },
  {
    "text": "In both scenarios, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=366"
  },
  {
    "text": "once a price change has been scheduled, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=368"
  },
  {
    "text": "you'll be able to review it until it goes into effect, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=371"
  },
  {
    "text": "alongside your current prices.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=374"
  },
  {
    "text": "And you can view details about your upcoming price change ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=377"
  },
  {
    "text": "by clicking on the drop-down next to the date of the change.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=379"
  },
  {
    "text": "However, note that once a price change goes into effect ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=384"
  },
  {
    "text": "on your scheduled date, it cannot be edited or undone.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=387"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you initially decide to preserve prices, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=392"
  },
  {
    "text": "you have the option to undo this action at a later time.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=394"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now let's talk about how you would initiate this ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=399"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the event you have subscribers ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=401"
  },
  {
    "text": "on multiple preserved prices.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=403"
  },
  {
    "text": "Keep in mind that if you have subscribers ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=405"
  },
  {
    "text": "on multiple preserved prices in the same territory, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=408"
  },
  {
    "text": "you can only increase a preserved price ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=411"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the next highest price.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=413"
  },
  {
    "text": "So if you decide to bring all subscribers on preserved prices ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=416"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the current price, start with the preserved price ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=419"
  },
  {
    "text": "closest to the current price and unpreserve it, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=422"
  },
  {
    "text": "then unpreserve the next highest price, and so on.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=425"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's take a look at an example.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=429"
  },
  {
    "text": "This developer is looking to increase ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=432"
  },
  {
    "text": "multiple preserved customer cohorts to the 3.99 price point, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=434"
  },
  {
    "text": "which is the price they currently have displayed ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=439"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the store.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=441"
  },
  {
    "text": "They'll start by increasing the price of their 2.99 cohort ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=444"
  },
  {
    "text": "since it's the closest group to the current price.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=448"
  },
  {
    "text": "As you can see here, the new price of 3.99 ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=451"
  },
  {
    "text": "goes into effect on February 1.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=455"
  },
  {
    "text": "Next, they'll bring the 1.99 cohort ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=458"
  },
  {
    "text": "up to the current price of 3.99 on March 1, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=461"
  },
  {
    "text": "and all of their customers will now be paying the same price ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=465"
  },
  {
    "text": "for their subscription.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=468"
  },
  {
    "text": "While this example shows price increases occurring ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=470"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the first of the month, note that you have the ability ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=473"
  },
  {
    "text": "to choose whatever date works best for your business.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=476"
  },
  {
    "text": "To initiate a price increase on a preserved cohort, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=480"
  },
  {
    "text": "click the date of the price change ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=484"
  },
  {
    "text": "that occurred closest to your current price.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=486"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then, click Edit Price.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=490"
  },
  {
    "text": "And select the territories ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=493"
  },
  {
    "text": "where you want to unpreserve the price.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=495"
  },
  {
    "text": "Click Next.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=498"
  },
  {
    "text": "Review the changes and click Confirm.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=501"
  },
  {
    "text": "You'll then repeat these steps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=505"
  },
  {
    "text": "for subscribers on other preserved prices, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=507"
  },
  {
    "text": "starting with the next price closest to the current price.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=510"
  },
  {
    "text": "Now, let's look at how to plan a price decrease.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=515"
  },
  {
    "text": "We'll start again in the Subscription Pricing section ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=519"
  },
  {
    "text": "of App Store Connect.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=522"
  },
  {
    "text": "Click on the plus button, then click on ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=524"
  },
  {
    "text": "Plan Subscription Price Change from the drop-down menu.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=528"
  },
  {
    "text": "Select the territories where you want to decrease the price.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=533"
  },
  {
    "text": "Once you've made your selection, click Next.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=537"
  },
  {
    "text": "You'll then choose the date ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=541"
  },
  {
    "text": "you'd like to begin your price decrease, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=542"
  },
  {
    "text": "followed by the currency and new price.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=545"
  },
  {
    "text": "Then, click Next.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=548"
  },
  {
    "text": "Again, you'll be prompted to review the price changes ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=551"
  },
  {
    "text": "in each territory and optionally set different prices ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=554"
  },
  {
    "text": "per territory.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=557"
  },
  {
    "text": "Once you've completed your review of pricing ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=559"
  },
  {
    "text": "in each region, click Next.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=561"
  },
  {
    "text": "You will then be prompted to confirm ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=565"
  },
  {
    "text": "your upcoming price decreases by clicking Confirm.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=566"
  },
  {
    "text": "In the event that any current subscribers ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=571"
  },
  {
    "text": "are paying higher than the new price, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=573"
  },
  {
    "text": "they will automatically renew at the lower price.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=575"
  },
  {
    "text": "Your price decrease will then go into effect ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=579"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the scheduled date.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=582"
  },
  {
    "text": "Note that if you want to decrease the price ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=584"
  },
  {
    "text": "of your subscription, the price will decrease ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=586"
  },
  {
    "text": "for all subscribers and you can't preserve ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=588"
  },
  {
    "text": "any higher-priced cohorts.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=590"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's take a look at another example.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=595"
  },
  {
    "text": "Here the developer has chosen to reduce the price ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=598"
  },
  {
    "text": "of their subscription to 99 cents starting on March 1.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=601"
  },
  {
    "text": "Since that price is cheaper ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=606"
  },
  {
    "text": "than all of their existing pricing cohorts, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=607"
  },
  {
    "text": "all customers will be brought down ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=610"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the new price starting on March 1.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=612"
  },
  {
    "text": "Finally, let's talk about how you can edit ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=617"
  },
  {
    "text": "your upcoming price changes before they go into effect.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=620"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you decide you no longer need the price change to occur, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=624"
  },
  {
    "text": "click Delete Price Change or click Edit Price Change ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=628"
  },
  {
    "text": "to make your necessary modifications.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=633"
  },
  {
    "text": "You'll then be able to make edits ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=637"
  },
  {
    "text": "to the regions where your price change will occur, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=638"
  },
  {
    "text": "the date your price change will begin, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=642"
  },
  {
    "text": "and your new subscription price.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=644"
  },
  {
    "text": "You can also automate many elements ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=648"
  },
  {
    "text": "of subscription price management with the App Store Connect API.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=650"
  },
  {
    "text": "For more information on all of the topics discussed today, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=656"
  },
  {
    "text": "please visit our developer website, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=660"
  },
  {
    "text": "which has a number of resources for you to review.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=662"
  },
  {
    "text": "And that concludes today's presentation.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=666"
  },
  {
    "text": "We hope this has helped you understand the necessary steps ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=669"
  },
  {
    "text": "to take when choosing to initiate a price change ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=672"
  },
  {
    "text": "for your business.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-110350/?time=674"
  }
]